#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:15
#: 7309fd67735c42baa5b48bf55724b859
msgid "Ai-WB2系列模组支持哪些开发方式"
msgstr "What development methods are supported by Ai-WB2 series modules?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:16
#: 3361210ed5a3439781a30cbcc5310407
msgid "AT开发，window环境和liunx环境开发"
msgstr ""
"AT development, development in Windows environment, and development in Linux "
"environment."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:19
#: 54e91d867e7a49ce90d6073928ebb677
msgid "Ai-WB2-32S模组与ESP32-S模组有什么区别，软硬件能否兼容"
msgstr ""
"What are the differences between the Ai-WB2-32S module and the ESP32-S "
"module? Are the software and hardware compatible?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:20
#: 32fc1f08c32b45a5a44e6e5d86554884
msgid ""
"Ai-WB2-32模组与ESP32-S模组封装兼容，但是引脚定义不一样；软件上所使用的芯片也"
"不一样，WB2-32S使用的是BL602芯片，ESP32模组使用的是ESP32D0WD芯片"
msgstr ""
"The Ai-WB2-32 module is package-compatible with the ESP32-S module, but the "
"pin definitions are different. In terms of software, the chips used are also "
"different. The WB2-32S uses the BL602 chip, while the ESP32 module uses the "
"ESP32D0WD chip."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:23
#: ef1460815cb4463b8df464a3d816129e
msgid "WB2模组支持WAPI协议吗"
msgstr "Does the WB2 module support the WAPI protocol?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:24
#: 25c3c8b5ecb84b65a124f35650f8133b
msgid "支持，不过需要通过二次开发实现"
msgstr "Yes, but it needs to be implemented through secondary development."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:27
#: 919951991e3e402db4af8e1a445aed58
msgid "WB2系列模组在做干扰规避测试项，表格上因填写什么参数"
msgstr ""
"When performing the interference avoidance test item for WB2 series modules, "
"what parameters should be filled in the table?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:28
#: b1772eb2e3754313b1b7b38630330f47
msgid "选择监测与避让"
msgstr "Select monitoring and avoidance."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:31
#: 5fe0f480dd224b6d91bf9c30ceb0810f
msgid "请问Ai-WB2-12F模组重新烧写固件的时候，EN引脚的电平设置情况如何？"
msgstr ""
"When reflashing firmware for the Ai-WB2-12F module, how should the EN pin "
"level be set?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:32
#: f42e0568dde9488fa64995f6828e15c8
msgid "当软件提示 “Please Press Reset Key” 的时候，将EN引脚拉低之后，再拉高"
msgstr ""
"When the software prompts “Please Press Reset Key”, pull the EN pin low, and "
"then pull it high again."

