#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:40
#: 3559916b297d48ac9bd7c5b626cf23ad
msgid "请问一下，我这边Ai-WB2-12F模组是否支持lua语言开发？"
msgstr "Does the Ai-WB2-12F module support Lua language development?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:41
#: 74f67732e01548d4b27f8527a52e2ebd
msgid "Ai-WB2-xx系列模组均不支持lua语言开发，仅8266系列支持；"
msgstr ""
"Ai-WB2-xx series modules do not support Lua language development. Only the "
"8266 series supports it."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:44
#: f8b3e2fca22e4220b16e2e1dffa0b9be
msgid "请问贵公司是否有rj45以太网网络透传功能的模组？"
msgstr ""
"Does your company have any module with RJ45 Ethernet network transparent "
"transmission function?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:45
#: 54b5c8c11f25477b83e440c09fe3acd7
msgid "没有。"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:48
#: 21c9aa87a27a4afb9b62e4f3c76df866
msgid "请问程序存储空间与我申请的flash空间是否会有冲突？"
msgstr ""
"Will the program storage space conflict with the flash space I apply for?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:49
#: f8f7facb0a914b0dab59d6f027e8b07a
msgid "不会，空间的分化由分区表决定，编译器中已做了防冲突功能；"
msgstr ""
"No. Space allocation is determined by the partition table, and the compiler "
"already includes an anti-conflict mechanism."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:52
#: 9be3ae97ace04e81ad71fd28fe22177e
msgid "WB2系列模组可以用ESP-IDF开发吗？"
msgstr "Can WB2 series modules be developed using ESP-IDF?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:53
#: 2d1bb0b6fab244c2acb38abc62b30b86
msgid "不可以，芯片方案不同"
msgstr "No. The chip solutions are different."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:56
#: 116fd8eec5e74515875f3b073f2b8ba4
msgid "WB2-07S模组天线是蓝牙的还是WIFI的，还是两个共用天线"
msgstr ""
"Is the antenna of the WB2-07S module for Bluetooth or Wi-Fi, or do they "
"share one antenna?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:57
#: 3dbeff11eb944fb5b04badc1f810f5b0
msgid "BLE和WIFI共用一条天线，分时复用"
msgstr "BLE and Wi-Fi share one antenna and use time-division multiplexing."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:60
#: 278f2c0dda2c4f1dae5768c37b22b374
msgid "请问WB2-32S是否支持arduino开发？"
msgstr "Does the WB2-32S support Arduino development?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:61
#: 1106c5c727914f3da2443fa8e579922f
msgid "不支持"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:64
#: 1554245d21984ea094a211ba365269ff
msgid "请问WB2模组是用的什么内核？"
msgstr "What core does the WB2 module use?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:65
#: 02ec558c69fd444797fdf66b92466165
msgid "RISC-V"
msgstr "RISC-V."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:68
#: 9502c7da49bd4b9b995d23eb42b3f15c
msgid "请问WB2模组支持空中升级么？"
msgstr "Does the WB2 module support over-the-air upgrade?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:69
#: 363fec90178a4b9395049e485a6dcf9a
msgid "支持OTA"
msgstr "Yes, it supports OTA."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:72
#: a3da4d4623b94f869955942172458b81
msgid "请问WB2模组有16M闪存的么？"
msgstr "Is there a WB2 module with 16M flash?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:73
#: 4c6ddc3e035e4bec9c0baaa31a4e71f7
msgid "通用的是2M与4M版本，16M需求的需联系商务定制；"
msgstr ""
"The common versions are 2M and 4M. For 16M requirements, please contact "
"sales for customization."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:76
#: 60159b7a45aa414e89ebe26ac99f85c3
msgid "WB2系列模块能传输水下的视频吗"
msgstr "Can WB2 series modules transmit underwater video?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:77
#: a38d14c046a94cfc839b827492a05a51
msgid "不支持，水下会吸收一部分的WIFI信号"
msgstr "No. Underwater environments absorb part of the Wi-Fi signal."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:80
#: 87fb58a565e34d9d9a3efd1d53546a26
msgid "Ai-WB2-32S开发板支持TinyGo吗"
msgstr "Does the Ai-WB2-32S development board support TinyGo?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:81
#: c88b322099164f34b4007db0470aebef
msgid "目前不支持Go语言开发"
msgstr "Go language development is not currently supported."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:84
#: fb00f1bb647449748b76ffb41f662a7e
msgid "WB2模块使用单行模式发送数据遇到0x0A会数据异常，应该怎样处理"
msgstr ""
"When the WB2 module uses single-line mode to send data, data becomes "
"abnormal when encountering 0x0A. How should this be handled?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:85
#: b6402fc6dba64425aee59632da38fe8e
msgid ""
"由于单行模式的指令判断0D 0A为结束符，故可以使用另外一条指令AT+SOCKETSEND进行"
"发送"
msgstr ""
"Because the command in single-line mode determines 0D 0A as the terminator, "
"you can use another command, AT+SOCKETSEND, to send the data."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:88
#: 26da382c05034a1c80cc2a5acbb7421b
msgid "请问WB2系列模组的SDK编译完成以后的固件是合并的还是分散的呢？"
msgstr ""
"After the SDK compilation of WB2 series modules is completed, is the "
"firmware merged or separated?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:89
#: 2c8cfcc72fb8496eb386fe5b42207a7d
msgid "是分散的"
msgstr "It is separated."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:92
#: 6f019a326c2049b1b2bd63c0451fa620
msgid "WB2-12F跟BW16引脚兼容吗"
msgstr "Are the pins of WB2-12F and BW16 compatible?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:93
#: 4f7b86fff983486681ba2648974014ac
msgid "AT固件的脚位兼容，可以无缝切换使用"
msgstr ""
"The pins of the AT firmware are compatible and can be switched seamlessly."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:96
#: 0f0887d82aba4cf5b8aa25154a8b46dc
msgid "WB2-12F可以直接移植ESP-12F的代码吗"
msgstr "Can ESP-12F code be directly ported to WB2-12F?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:97
#: 943e70c129d94583b931fe9e1f989143
msgid "不可以直接移植，需要基于WB2的SDK进行修改"
msgstr ""
"No. It cannot be directly ported. It needs to be modified based on the WB2 "
"SDK."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:100
#: 49d76cd54f374599b690c92217a92d4b
msgid "WB2系列模组支持BLE MESH与其他品牌的BLE MESH可通配使用吗"
msgstr ""
"Can the BLE MESH function of WB2 series modules be used interchangeably with "
"BLE MESH from other brands?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:101
#: a1e6617e887649968b8803de2657ca67
msgid "MESH功能需要做开发实现  AT固件没有该功能"
msgstr ""
"The MESH function needs to be implemented through development. The AT "
"firmware does not have this function."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:104
#: a14b71d1289f45c98d11dd19e8261c9e
msgid "WB2-07S的GPIO接口，模块内部有没有上拉电阻"
msgstr ""
"Do the GPIO interfaces of the WB2-07S have internal pull-up resistors inside "
"the module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:105
#: 4c33860273fa4db3b01bd413d1fe6889
msgid "模组内部的GPIO没有接上拉电阻"
msgstr "The GPIOs inside the module are not connected to pull-up resistors."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:108
#: fc42549b0e09412a9826ea1f38634aee
msgid "ESP8266二次开发中的eagle.flash文件该如何生成"
msgstr ""
"How is the eagle.flash file generated during secondary development of "
"ESP8266?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:109
#: ac5e10c44046424b81572e5d093076fa
msgid "在编译规则中，APP选项选择为0，表示不使用OTA功能"
msgstr ""
"In the compilation rules, set the APP option to 0, indicating that OTA is "
"not used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:112
#: 40cae71414a944cc89562bab60d27a7d
msgid "8266模块频繁出现wdt reset该如何解决"
msgstr "How to solve frequent wdt reset on the 8266 module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:113
#: fcf787c0ffaa444eb40ad738871dad2d
msgid "检查供电电源，禁止使用USB转TTL串口板进行供电"
msgstr ""
"Check the power supply. Do not use a USB-to-TTL serial board for power "
"supply."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:116
#: 094baab85fd64e08b7f0428f13560d49
msgid "请问有支持NFC配网的WiFi模块么？"
msgstr "Are there any Wi-Fi modules that support NFC provisioning?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:117
#: c23cf22e748e4e7892afe5c0dbe93a14
msgid "目前没有；"
msgstr "Not currently."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:120
#: 0a21bac4179a43eea19f12729ee02d09
msgid "请问我二次开发固件SPI烧录模式要配置成什么呢？QIO么？"
msgstr ""
"What SPI flashing mode should be configured for secondary development "
"firmware? QIO?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:121
#: f11ec01bb3a1412da36732db82d24d64
msgid "有二次开发所配置的SPI模式决定；"
msgstr "It is determined by the SPI mode configured for secondary development."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:124
#: ce2f37fb0f69454f8e9eb74d52dc311b
msgid "WB2系列出厂固件支持在线升级吗"
msgstr "Does the factory firmware of the WB2 series support online upgrade?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:125
#: 47dc12b7bf9643e28350b0c98d68e12a
msgid "支持，可以通过发送OTA指令进行在线升级操作"
msgstr "Yes. Online upgrade can be performed by sending OTA commands."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:128
#: bd613003429d4f6dab1b11a576efa33a
msgid "请问有WB2系列模组开发的API说明文档么？"
msgstr "Is there an API documentation for WB2 series module development?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:129
#: 3424c947fd5c44d9aa16ddd4a42e3495
msgid ""
"有的，查看 `(查看链接)  <https://wb2-api-web.readthedocs.io/en/latest/>`__"
msgstr "Yes. See `(link)  <https://wb2-api-web.readthedocs.io/en/latest/>`__"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:132
#: bcc34ac6f2994c999ec92c89510b3f67
msgid "请问为何WB2-12S模组发送指令没有任何反应？"
msgstr "Why does the WB2-12S module not respond to commands?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:133
#: cdb94a5f84c4463893091e3339ffd998
msgid ""
"若是上电有启动信息，则检查一下RX口是否没接稳，或者接错了。若是没有启动信息，"
"则串口部分有问题，要排查问题。"
msgstr ""
"If there is startup information after power-on, check whether the RX pin is "
"loose or connected incorrectly. If there is no startup information, there is "
"an issue with the serial port part, and troubleshooting is required."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:136
#: 0e3850ab60bd4cfe80be7ef84bda907b
msgid "请问模组底部的大焊盘需要接地么？还是悬空？"
msgstr ""
"Should the large pad at the bottom of the module be grounded or left "
"floating?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/other.rst:137
#: 435c0671860d408ca062a6d1c393766f
msgid "建议直接接地，有助于散热。"
msgstr ""
"It is recommended to connect it directly to ground, which helps with heat "
"dissipation."
